NAME: Not Specified
DESCRIPTION: Gender is not specified or not received. If no gender value is received, then this is the system default value.

NAME: Other
DESCRIPTION: Gender is Other. Value may be used to differeniate as neither Male or Female.

NAME: Unknown
DESCRIPTION: Gender is Unknown. Value may be used to signify that gender is unknown at the time.

NAME: Transgender
DESCRIPTION: A person whose gender identity or gender expression differs from their assigned sex.

NAME: Intersex
DESCRIPTION: A person (one of unisexual specimens) who is born with genitalia and/or secondary sexual characteristics of indeterminate sex, or which combine features of both sexes.

NAME: Prefer Not to Answer
DESCRIPTION: A response indicating that an individual prefers or preferred not to answer.
